text: FIFA 20 is a 2019 association football simulation video game in Electronic Arts' FIFA series created by EA Vancouver and published by Electronic Arts. It was released for the Playstation 4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, Google Stadia and Microsoft Windows.
